OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO STATE AFFAIRS AND GOVERNMENT -- THE RHODE ISLAND
LOBBYING REFORM ACT
***
1 This act would prohibit lobbyists from making any political contributions to any member
2 of the general assembly from January 1 through July 1 in any year, unless the general assembly
3 adjourns for the year prior to July 1.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
